{"tid":1072931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電視圈一大損失！阮兆祥祥師兄疑似離巢無綫","createTime":"2019-03-22T10:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T07:13:13.000Z","uid":92376,"like":351,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6850dd3325d53043da4cdb0085eb267e14ce46","tid":1072931,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"過往在無綫演出過無數經典劇的阮兆祥，有指他已在今個月靜悄悄滿約無綫，就連無綫官方網站的藝人欄亦未見其照片。 <br />\n<br />\n祥仔1984年加入無綫，雖然曾於1997年離巢，但之後又重投娘家懷抱，演出過《溏心風暴》、《皆大歡喜》、《巨輪》等經典劇；他又夥曾志偉曾參《獎門人》系列，並於2009年萬千星輝頒獎典禮奪最佳節目主持，是無綫難得笑匠。 <br />\n<br />\n其實近年的阮兆祥產量不多，去年僅得一套劇集《平安谷之詭谷傳說》，但亦有於電台主持節目，早前又與夏雨、米雪等到新加坡演出舞台劇，再加上經常返內地商演，故收入應該也相當不錯。東網就離巢一事聯絡阮兆祥，惟尚未接獲回覆。 <br />\n<br />\nNo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f175877b40600ee454bc573ca7f437275ff8faf","tid":1072931,"uid":181318,"like":554,"dislike":29,"score":525,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"零觀眾緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23043159f5a9086bae818388bf6254a509501803","tid":1072931,"uid":92376,"like":23,"dislike":180,"score":-157,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"祥仔演得又唱得 唔好走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為食神探麥犀哥型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ae4c22d7e588588776a8e8eb58a2c5b384471c","tid":1072931,"uid":92376,"like":626,"dislike":62,"score":564,"quote":{"pid":"0f175877b40600ee454bc573ca7f437275ff8faf","tid":1072931,"uid":181318,"like":554,"dislike":29,"score":525,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"零觀眾緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"你就0<br />\n當年一句不知淥死誰手+哈哈哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n到依家連登仔都仲好記憶猶新<img src=\"/assets/fac